Date:   Thu Dec 1 08:33:39 2022 +0100

    One namespace for component's Pipeline-as-Code CI (#968)
    
    Unify .tekton directories into tekton-ci component.
    
    Reasons:
    - Shared-resources should not be used anymore, which would require to
      create/manage secret in each namespace. With one namespaces it would
      be managed only there
    - SRE engineers are interested in the service, so they will see only the
      service in the service namespace - not pods of CI pipelines
    - Quota can be set on service namespace, CI pipelineRuns will not take
      resources from it
    - In case of multiple environments we can select one when the CI will be
      installed, as part of the commit the CI is disabled for developemnt
      environment

